1
00:00:04,463 --> 00:00:07,716
Kirk: CAPTAIN'S LOG,
STARDATE 5928.5.

2
00:00:07,758 --> 00:00:09,635
THE "ENTERPRISE" HAS RECEIVED
A DISTRESS CALL

3
00:00:09,677 --> 00:00:11,637
FROM A GROUP OF SCIENTISTS
ON CAMUS II

4
00:00:11,679 --> 00:00:14,556
WHO WERE EXPLORING THE RUINS
OF A DEAD CIVILIZATION.

5
00:00:14,598 --> 00:00:17,017
THEIR SITUATION
IS DESPERATE.

6
00:00:17,058 --> 00:00:18,101
TWO OF THE SURVIVORS ARE

7
00:00:18,143 --> 00:00:20,521
THE EXPEDITION SURGEON
DR. COLEMAN

8
00:00:20,562 --> 00:00:22,439
AND THE LEADER
OF THE EXPEDITION,

9
00:00:22,481 --> 00:00:24,608
DR. JANICE LESTER.

10
00:00:24,650 --> 00:00:25,776
WHAT'S WRONG
WITH HER?

11
00:00:25,818 --> 00:00:27,778
EXPOSURE
TO RADIATION.

12
00:00:27,820 --> 00:00:29,571
WHAT FORM OF RADIATION
WAS IT?

13
00:00:29,613 --> 00:00:32,574
NOTHING I'VE EVER
ENCOUNTERED.

14
00:00:32,616 --> 00:00:34,660
[DR. LESTER MOANS]

15
00:00:42,001 --> 00:00:43,084
JANICE...

16
00:00:45,671 --> 00:00:48,632
YOU MUST REMAIN
ABSOLUTELY QUIET.

17
00:00:48,674 --> 00:00:50,342
THOSE ARE DOCTOR'S
ORDERS, NOT MINE.

18
00:00:53,052 --> 00:00:55,138
Spock: CAPTAIN,
TRICORDER PICKING UP

19
00:00:55,180 --> 00:00:56,640
VERY FAINT
LIFE READINGS

20
00:00:56,682 --> 00:00:59,810
APPROXIMATELY
700 METERS FROM HERE.

21
00:00:59,852 --> 00:01:02,521
HELP WILL
HAVE TO BE IMMEDIATE.

22
00:01:02,563 --> 00:01:05,733
UH...UH...

23
00:01:05,774 --> 00:01:07,484
PERHAPS YOUR PRESENCE
WILL QUIET HER.

24
00:01:18,286 --> 00:01:21,122
I HOPED I WOULDN'T
SEE YOU AGAIN.

25
00:01:21,164 --> 00:01:22,666
I DON'T BLAME YOU.

26
00:01:22,708 --> 00:01:25,293
THE YEAR
WE WERE TOGETHER
AT STARFLEET

27
00:01:25,335 --> 00:01:28,714
IS THE ONLY TIME
IN MY LIFE
I WAS ALIVE.

28
00:01:28,756 --> 00:01:31,675
I NEVER STOPPED YOU
FROM GOING ON
WITH YOUR SPACE WORK.

29
00:01:31,717 --> 00:01:35,679
YOUR WORLD OF
STARSHIP CAPTAINS
DOESN'T ADMIT WOMEN.

30
00:01:37,848 --> 00:01:39,391
IT ISN'T FAIR.

31
00:01:39,433 --> 00:01:41,268
NO, IT ISN'T,

32
00:01:41,309 --> 00:01:44,688
AND YOU PUNISHED
AND TORTURED ME
BECAUSE OF IT.

33
00:01:49,109 --> 00:01:50,652
I LOVED YOU.

34
00:01:52,654 --> 00:01:55,866
WE COULD HAVE ROAMED
AMONG THE STARS.

35
00:01:55,908 --> 00:01:57,451
WE'D HAVE KILLED
EACH OTHER.

36
00:02:00,203 --> 00:02:01,288
IT MIGHT
HAVE BEEN BETTER.

37
00:02:25,646 --> 00:02:27,188
[BEAM FIRES]

38
00:03:13,110 --> 00:03:15,654
Kirk: SPACE--THE FINAL FRONTIER.

39
00:03:21,869 --> 00:03:26,289
THESE ARE THE VOYAGES
OF THE STARSHIP "ENTERPRISE,"

40
00:03:26,331 --> 00:03:27,791
ITS 5-YEAR MISSION--

41
00:03:27,833 --> 00:03:30,460
TO EXPLORE
STRANGE NEW WORLDS...

42
00:03:30,502 --> 00:03:34,422
TO SEEK OUT NEW LIFE
AND NEW CIVILIZATIONS...

43
00:03:34,464 --> 00:03:37,342
TO BOLDLY GO WHERE
NO MAN HAS GONE BEFORE.

44
00:04:34,108 --> 00:04:36,568
[LAUGHING]

45
00:04:36,610 --> 00:04:38,319
YOU HAD YOUR CHANCE,
CAPTAIN KIRK.

46
00:04:38,361 --> 00:04:39,863
YOU SHOULD HAVE SMOTHERED
THE LIFE IN ME.

47
00:04:39,905 --> 00:04:41,156
THEN THEY WOULD HAVE SAID,

48
00:04:41,198 --> 00:04:44,284
DR. JANICE LESTER DIED
OF RADIATION POISONING

49
00:04:44,325 --> 00:04:45,619
IN THE LINE OF DUTY.

50
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:47,913
WHY DIDN'T YOU DO IT?
YOU ALWAYS WANTED TO.

51
00:04:47,955 --> 00:04:49,372
DIDN'T YOU?

52
00:04:52,167 --> 00:04:54,002
YOU HAD THE STRENGTH
TO DO IT.

53
00:04:57,089 --> 00:04:58,381
BUT YOU WERE AFRAID.

54
00:04:58,423 --> 00:05:00,341
YOU WERE ALWAYS AFRAID.

55
00:05:00,383 --> 00:05:04,221
NOW JANICE LESTER TAKES
THE PLACE OF CAPTAIN KIRK.

56
00:05:07,682 --> 00:05:09,226
I ALREADY POSSESS
YOUR PHYSICAL STRENGTH.

57
00:05:12,938 --> 00:05:16,024
ONLY THIS...CAPTAIN KIRK

58
00:05:16,066 --> 00:05:17,859
IS NOT AFRAID TO KILL.

59
00:05:17,901 --> 00:05:19,319
[MOANS]

60
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:23,282
NOW YOU'LL KNOW
THE INDIGNITY
OF BEING A WOMAN.

61
00:05:23,323 --> 00:05:26,243
[MOANING]

62
00:05:26,285 --> 00:05:29,997
FOR YOU, THIS AGONY
WILL SOON PASS,
AS IT HAS FOR ME.

63
00:05:30,038 --> 00:05:32,916
QUIET. QUIET!

64
00:05:32,958 --> 00:05:36,503
BELIEVE ME,
IT'S BETTER TO BE DEAD...

65
00:05:36,544 --> 00:05:40,215
THAN TO LIVE ALONE
IN THE BODY OF A WOMAN.

66
00:05:40,257 --> 00:05:41,508
[THUD]
IT'S BETTER TO BE DEAD.

67
00:05:44,928 --> 00:05:46,054
[FOOTSTEPS]

68
00:05:57,565 --> 00:05:59,818
DR. McCOY...

69
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:01,486
YOUR REPORT.

70
00:06:01,528 --> 00:06:02,570
WE WERE
TOO LATE, JIM.

71
00:06:02,612 --> 00:06:04,323
THERE'S NOTHING
COULD BE DONE.

72
00:06:04,363 --> 00:06:08,160
WAS IT RADIATION,
AS SUGGESTED?

73
00:06:08,202 --> 00:06:09,870
NO, I BELIEVE
IT WAS CELEBIUM.

74
00:06:09,911 --> 00:06:11,955
HOWEVER, DR. COLEMAN
DISAGREES.

75
00:06:11,997 --> 00:06:14,624
TO BE SPECIFIC
IS ESSENTIAL

76
00:06:14,666 --> 00:06:15,959
BECAUSE THE TREATMENT
OF CELEBIUM IS QUITE--

77
00:06:16,001 --> 00:06:17,044
DR. McCOY.

78
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:23,717
DID YOU NOTICE
ANY UNUSUAL SYMPTOMS
WHILE WE WERE GONE?

79
00:06:23,758 --> 00:06:25,802
NO, NOTHING AT ALL.
SHE WAS UNCONSCIOUS
ALL THE TIME.

80
00:06:32,433 --> 00:06:34,978
DR. LESTER
IS NEAR DEATH.

81
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:38,732
PERHAPS THE SHOCK
OF KNOWING WHAT
HAPPENED TO HER STAFF

82
00:06:38,773 --> 00:06:40,734
IS PART OF THE PROBLEM.

83
00:06:40,775 --> 00:06:42,652
I'M SURE IT IS.

84
00:06:42,694 --> 00:06:45,572
BEAMING HER UP TO
THE "ENTERPRISE" WOULD BE
LESS HARMFUL THAN WAITING.

85
00:06:45,613 --> 00:06:47,908
I--I DON'T KNOW.
I'M NOT SURE.

86
00:06:58,210 --> 00:07:00,212
CAPTAIN KIRK
TO THE "ENTERPRISE."

87
00:07:00,254 --> 00:07:02,172
CAPTAIN KIRK
TO THE "ENTERPRISE."

88
00:07:02,214 --> 00:07:03,548
Scotty:
MR. SCOTT, SIR.

89
00:07:03,590 --> 00:07:05,842
SCOTT...

90
00:07:05,884 --> 00:07:07,928
PREPARE TO BEAM
THE LANDING PARTY ABOARD,

91
00:07:07,969 --> 00:07:09,763
PLUS TWO OTHERS,
ONE CRITICALLY ILL.

92
00:07:09,804 --> 00:07:12,849
HAVE A MEDICAL TEAM
STANDING BY TO RECEIVE
THE PATIENT.

93
00:07:12,891 --> 00:07:14,393
CAPTAIN KIRK OUT.

94
00:07:18,063 --> 00:07:19,147
PREPARE TO BEAM ABOARD.

95
00:07:30,491 --> 00:07:33,203
DR. COLEMAN,
ACCOMPANY THE PATIENT
TO THE SICK BAY.

96
00:07:35,914 --> 00:07:38,375
MR. SPOCK, TAKE
THE SHIP OUT OF ORBIT.

97
00:07:38,417 --> 00:07:41,336
RESUME
DESIGNATED COURSE.

98
00:07:41,378 --> 00:07:42,963
DR. McCOY.

99
00:07:43,004 --> 00:07:46,633
DR. McCOY,
YOU AND DR. COLEMAN

100
00:07:46,674 --> 00:07:48,885
SEEM TO DISAGREE
ON DIAGNOSIS.

101
00:07:48,927 --> 00:07:51,596
NO, NOT ENTIRELY.
WE BOTH AGREE
IT'S RADIATION.

102
00:07:51,638 --> 00:07:54,766
DR. COLEMAN
ISN'T PREPARED TO SAY
WHAT FORM OF RADIATION.

103
00:07:54,808 --> 00:07:57,602
WILL IT AFFECT
YOUR ARRIVING AT
A CORRECT TREATMENT?

104
00:07:57,644 --> 00:08:00,981
IT'S CRUCIAL.

105
00:08:01,022 --> 00:08:02,232
WELL...

106
00:08:02,274 --> 00:08:04,692
THIS IS ESPECIALLY
DISTURBING TO ME

107
00:08:04,734 --> 00:08:08,155
FOR...
PERSONAL REASONS.

108
00:08:08,196 --> 00:08:10,573
OH? I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU KNEW HER THAT WELL.

109
00:08:10,615 --> 00:08:14,286
OH, YES. IT'S
BEEN A LONG TIME
SINCE I SAW HER.

110
00:08:14,328 --> 00:08:16,955
I WALKED OUT ON HER
WHEN IT BECAME SERIOUS.

111
00:08:16,997 --> 00:08:21,293
WELL, YOU MUST HAVE BEEN
VERY YOUNG AT THE TIME, JIM.

112
00:08:21,335 --> 00:08:25,797
YOUTH DOESN'T
EXCUSE EVERYTHING,
DR. McCOY.

113
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:28,300
IT'S A VERY UNHAPPY
MEMORY FOR ME.

114
00:08:28,342 --> 00:08:29,884
OH, I DIDN'T
REALIZE THAT.

115
00:08:29,926 --> 00:08:31,886
I SHALL DO EVERYTHING
IN MY POWER.

116
00:08:31,928 --> 00:08:33,680
THANK YOU.
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

117
00:08:37,434 --> 00:08:40,979
DR. LESTER IS CERTAINLY
A VERY LUCKY YOUNG PERSON

118
00:08:41,021 --> 00:08:42,605
TO HAVE ESCAPED.

119
00:08:42,647 --> 00:08:44,649
YES, VERY LUCKY.

120
00:08:44,691 --> 00:08:45,733
VERY LUCKY.

121
00:08:50,655 --> 00:08:52,699
[MOANING]

122
00:09:06,046 --> 00:09:07,130
IT JUST BEGAN.

123
00:09:07,172 --> 00:09:08,715
WELL, YOU BETTER PUT
A STOP TO IT!

124
00:09:08,756 --> 00:09:11,676
IF YOU ALLOW DR. LESTER
TO BECOME FULLY CONSCIOUS,

125
00:09:11,718 --> 00:09:13,053
SHE'LL KNOW
WHAT HAS HAPPENED.

126
00:09:13,094 --> 00:09:15,138
PROBABLY NO ONE
WILL BELIEVE IT.

127
00:09:15,180 --> 00:09:16,139
PROBABLY?

128
00:09:16,181 --> 00:09:19,142
THAT'S ALL
WE CAN ASK FOR.

129
00:09:19,184 --> 00:09:21,644
HOW CAN DEATH
BE EXPLAINED NOW?

130
00:09:21,686 --> 00:09:23,771
[MOANING]

131
00:09:23,813 --> 00:09:25,524
I TELL YOU,
IT CAN'T CONTINUE.

132
00:09:25,565 --> 00:09:28,276
YOU KILLED EVERY ONE
OF THE STAFF.

133
00:09:28,318 --> 00:09:29,361
YOU SENT THEM
WHERE YOU KNEW

134
00:09:29,403 --> 00:09:31,863
THE CELEBIUM
SHIELDING WAS WEAK.

135
00:09:31,905 --> 00:09:33,073
NOW, WHY DIDN'T YOU
KILL HIM?

136
00:09:33,114 --> 00:09:35,950
YOU HAD THE PERFECT
OPPORTUNITY.

137
00:09:35,992 --> 00:09:38,078
THERE WASN'T ENOUGH TIME.

138
00:09:38,119 --> 00:09:42,249
I GAVE YOU
EVERY MINUTE
YOU ASKED FOR.

139
00:09:42,290 --> 00:09:44,792
HE HUNG ON
TO LIFE TOO HARD.
I COULDN'T--

140
00:09:44,834 --> 00:09:47,003
YOU COULDN'T BECAUSE
YOU LOVE HIM.

141
00:09:47,045 --> 00:09:49,672
YOU WANT ME TO BE
HIS MURDERER.

142
00:09:49,714 --> 00:09:52,384
LOVE...HIM?

143
00:09:52,426 --> 00:09:54,052
I LOVE THE LIFE HE LED,

144
00:09:54,094 --> 00:09:57,638
THE POWER OF
A STARSHIP COMMANDER.

145
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:59,724
IT'S MY LIFE NOW.

146
00:09:59,766 --> 00:10:01,935
I WON'T BECOME
A MURDERER.

147
00:10:01,976 --> 00:10:03,144
YOU ARE A MURDERER!

148
00:10:07,482 --> 00:10:08,567
YOU KNEW
IT WAS CELEBIUM.

149
00:10:08,608 --> 00:10:10,110
YOU COULD HAVE
TREATED THEM FOR IT.

150
00:10:10,151 --> 00:10:11,986
YOU'RE A MURDERER
MANY TIMES OVER.

151
00:10:12,028 --> 00:10:14,072
[MOANING]

152
00:10:17,325 --> 00:10:18,826
JIM, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

153
00:10:18,868 --> 00:10:20,995
I THOUGHT MY PRESENCE
MIGHT QUIET DR. LESTER.

154
00:10:21,037 --> 00:10:22,247
IT SEEMS TO HAVE HAD
THE OPPOSITE EFFECT.

155
00:10:22,289 --> 00:10:24,165
IT HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH YOU.

156
00:10:24,207 --> 00:10:26,667
IT'S A SYMPTOM
OF THE DEVELOPING
RADIATION ILLNESS.

157
00:10:26,709 --> 00:10:28,336
TESTS WITH
THE SHIP'S EQUIPMENT

158
00:10:28,378 --> 00:10:32,173
SHOWS NO SIGNS OF
INTERNAL RADIATION
DAMAGE, DR. COLEMAN.

159
00:10:32,215 --> 00:10:37,387
DIDN'T DR. LESTER'S STAFF
BECOME DELIRIOUS BEFORE
THEY WENT OFF AND DIED?

160
00:10:37,429 --> 00:10:39,097
UH, YES, CAPTAIN, YES.

161
00:10:39,139 --> 00:10:42,309
DR. LESTER COULD BE
SUFFERING FROM
A PHASER STUN

162
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:45,353
AS FAR AS
THE SYMPTOMS
I CAN DETECT, JIM.

163
00:10:45,395 --> 00:10:47,397
DR. COLEMAN,

164
00:10:47,439 --> 00:10:49,774
DR. McCOY HAS HAD
A GREAT DEAL OF EXPERIENCE

165
00:10:49,816 --> 00:10:53,153
WITH RADIATION EXPOSURE
ON-BOARD THE "ENTERPRISE."

166
00:10:53,194 --> 00:10:55,863
I AM GUIDED
BY HIS OPINION.

167
00:10:55,905 --> 00:10:57,324
DR. LESTER
AND HER STAFF

168
00:10:57,365 --> 00:11:00,701
HAVE BEEN UNDER
MY SUPERVISION
FOR TWO YEARS NOW.

169
00:11:00,743 --> 00:11:03,121
IF YOU DON'T FOLLOW
MY RECOMMENDATIONS,

170
00:11:03,163 --> 00:11:07,041
RESPONSIBILITY
FOR HER HEALTH
OR HER DEATH...

171
00:11:07,083 --> 00:11:08,209
WILL BE YOURS.

172
00:11:11,671 --> 00:11:13,340
UH...

173
00:11:14,924 --> 00:11:17,636
DR. McCOY, I AM SORRY,

174
00:11:17,676 --> 00:11:19,346
BUT I'M GOING TO HAVE
TO TAKE YOU OFF THE CASE

175
00:11:19,387 --> 00:11:20,930
AND TURN IT OVER
TO DR. COLEMAN.

176
00:11:20,972 --> 00:11:22,265
YOU CAN'T DO THIS.

177
00:11:22,307 --> 00:11:25,602
ON THIS SHIP, MY MEDICAL
AUTHORITY IS FINAL.

178
00:11:25,644 --> 00:11:28,729
IF DR. COLEMAN WANTS TO ASSUME
THE FULL RESPONSIBILITY,
LET HIM DO IT.

179
00:11:28,771 --> 00:11:30,357
I WON'T ALLOW IT.
IT'S DONE.

180
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,028
DR. COLEMAN, YOUR PATIENT.

181
00:11:36,988 --> 00:11:38,823
UH... UH...

182
00:11:38,865 --> 00:11:42,035
DR. COLEMAN, DIDN'T YOU
SUGGEST A SEDATION
TO REST THE PATIENT?

183
00:11:42,076 --> 00:11:43,744
YES, CAPTAIN.
IT'S NOT NECESSARY,
JIM.

184
00:11:43,786 --> 00:11:45,455
CAN'T YOU SEE SHE'S
COMING AROUND?

185
00:11:45,497 --> 00:11:48,166
[MOANING]

186
00:11:55,507 --> 00:11:56,715
DR. COLEMAN?

187
00:11:56,757 --> 00:12:00,136
NURSE, ADMINISTER
THE SEDATIVE.

188
00:12:00,178 --> 00:12:02,681
A SEDATIVE IS NOT
WISE AT THIS TIME,
CAPTAIN.

189
00:12:02,721 --> 00:12:04,516
NURSE CHAPEL,
YOU HAVE YOUR ORDERS.

190
00:12:06,184 --> 00:12:08,311
NURSE CHAPEL,

191
00:12:08,353 --> 00:12:09,770
FOLLOW
YOUR INSTRUCTIONS.

192
00:12:22,701 --> 00:12:24,411
OH...

193
00:12:24,452 --> 00:12:26,996
AM I...
REALLY LOSING

194
00:12:27,038 --> 00:12:29,999
COMMAND OF
THE "ENTERPRISE"?

195
00:12:30,041 --> 00:12:31,501
NO.

196
00:12:31,543 --> 00:12:34,003
OH, NO. BAD DREAM.

197
00:12:34,045 --> 00:12:35,505
OH,
BAD DREAM.

198
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:52,939
Kirk's voice: JAMES KIRK IS
RETURNING TO CONSCIOUSNESS

199
00:12:52,980 --> 00:12:54,941
IN THE BODY OF JANICE LESTER.

200
00:12:54,982 --> 00:12:57,569
THE "ENTERPRISE" IS PROCEEDING
TO ITS NEXT MISSION

201
00:12:57,611 --> 00:13:00,280
ON THE COURSE SET FOR IT
BEFORE I TOOK OVER COMMAND.

202
00:13:00,321 --> 00:13:03,491
NOW THE YEARS I SPENT
STUDYING EVERY SINGLE DETAIL

203
00:13:03,533 --> 00:13:06,327
OF THE SHIP'S OPERATION
WILL BE TESTED.

204
00:13:06,369 --> 00:13:08,204
WITH A LITTLE EXPERIENCE,

205
00:13:08,246 --> 00:13:10,248
I WILL BE INVULNERABLE
TO SUSPICION.

206
00:13:21,134 --> 00:13:23,678
Kirk's voice: AT LAST I ATTAINED
WHAT IS MY JUST DUE--

207
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:25,722
COMMAND OF A STARSHIP,

208
00:13:25,764 --> 00:13:28,891
ALL THE MONTHS OF PREPARATION
NOW COME TO FRUITION.

209
00:13:37,609 --> 00:13:39,444
COURSE, MR. CHEKOV?

210
00:13:39,486 --> 00:13:43,239
127 MARK 8.

211
00:13:43,281 --> 00:13:46,326
MR. SULU, SET SPEED
AT WARP FACTOR 2.

212
00:13:46,367 --> 00:13:48,662
WARP FACTOR 2,
SIR.

213
00:13:48,703 --> 00:13:50,789
[INDISTINCT RADIO COMMUNICATIONS
IN BACKGROUND]

214
00:14:09,974 --> 00:14:11,225
MR. CHEKOV,

215
00:14:11,267 --> 00:14:13,894
PLOT A COURSE FOR
THE BENECIA COLONY.

216
00:14:13,936 --> 00:14:17,064
DIRECT COURSE
TO BENECIA--
373 MARK 8.

217
00:14:17,106 --> 00:14:19,651
HOW LONG TO THE COLONY
AT OUR PRESENT SPEED?

218
00:14:19,693 --> 00:14:21,778
48 HOURS, SIR.

219
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:24,405
MR. SULU, SET COURSE
FOR THE COLONY--

220
00:14:24,447 --> 00:14:25,906
373 MARK 8.

221
00:14:25,948 --> 00:14:27,283
AYE, SIR.

222
00:14:27,325 --> 00:14:29,910
373 MARK 8.

223
00:14:29,952 --> 00:14:32,372
CAPTAIN, THAT WILL DELAY
OUR WORK AT BETA AURIGAE.

224
00:14:32,413 --> 00:14:33,832
IT MEANS
REVERSING COURSE.

225
00:14:33,873 --> 00:14:36,083
YES, IT CAN'T BE HELPED.
WE MUST TAKE DR. LESTER

226
00:14:36,125 --> 00:14:37,418
TO A PLACE WHERE SHE
CAN BE TREATED.

227
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:38,919
MAY I POINT OUT
THAT STARBASE TWO

228
00:14:38,961 --> 00:14:41,214
IS ON THE DIRECT ROUTE
TO OUR DESTINATION?

229
00:14:43,508 --> 00:14:45,677
HOW LONG TO STARBASE TWO?

230
00:14:45,719 --> 00:14:47,595
72 HOURS, CAPTAIN.

231
00:14:47,637 --> 00:14:49,055
THAT'S 24 HOURS TOO LONG.

232
00:14:49,096 --> 00:14:52,266
DR. LESTER'S CONDITION
IS INCREASINGLY SERIOUS.

233
00:14:52,308 --> 00:14:53,476
CONTINUE PRESENT COURSE.

234
00:14:53,518 --> 00:14:55,978
AYE, SIR.

235
00:14:56,020 --> 00:14:58,606
SIR, IF THE DIAGNOSIS
OF DR. LESTER'S ILLNESS

236
00:14:58,648 --> 00:15:00,358
IS THE CRITICAL PROBLEM,

237
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:03,236
THEN THE BENECIA COLONY
IS DEFINITELY NOT
THE PLACE FOR HER.

238
00:15:03,277 --> 00:15:05,946
THEIR MEDICAL FACILITIES
ARE THE MOST PRIMITIVE.

239
00:15:05,988 --> 00:15:07,031
THEY WILL HAVE TO SERVE.

240
00:15:07,073 --> 00:15:09,450
STARBASE TWO
IS FULLY EQUIPPED

241
00:15:09,492 --> 00:15:11,828
AND STAFFED
WITH THE NECESSARY
SPECIALISTS

242
00:15:11,870 --> 00:15:15,832
TO DETERMINE EXACTLY
WHAT IS WRONG
WITH THE DOCTOR.

243
00:15:15,874 --> 00:15:18,501
IS THAT NOT CRUCIAL
TO YOUR DECISION?

244
00:15:18,543 --> 00:15:19,878
THANK YOU, MR. SPOCK,

245
00:15:19,919 --> 00:15:21,379
BUT THE FACILITIES
WILL BE OF LITTLE USE

246
00:15:21,421 --> 00:15:24,841
IF DR. LESTER'S DEAD.

247
00:15:24,883 --> 00:15:26,885
TIME IS OF THE ESSENCE.
CONTINUE PRESENT COURSE.

248
00:15:32,557 --> 00:15:34,851
AT MAXIMUM SPEED...

249
00:15:34,893 --> 00:15:37,019
STARBASE TWO WOULD STILL
MEET THE EMERGENCY.

250
00:15:43,192 --> 00:15:45,236
CAPTAIN, SHALL I ADVISE
STARFLEET COMMAND

251
00:15:45,278 --> 00:15:47,614
OF THE CHANGE OF PLAN?

252
00:15:47,655 --> 00:15:50,617
NO CHANGE OF PLAN HAS
BEEN ORDERED, LIEUTENANT.

253
00:15:50,658 --> 00:15:53,160
OUR ARRIVAL AT BETA AURIGAE
WILL MERELY BE DELAYED.

254
00:15:53,202 --> 00:15:56,205
OUR GRAVITATIONAL STUDIES
OF THAT BINARY SYSTEM
WILL NOT SUFFER,

255
00:15:56,247 --> 00:15:57,957
AND A LIFE MAY BE SAVED.

256
00:15:57,998 --> 00:16:00,418
THAT IS NOT UNUSUAL PROCEDURE
FOR THE "ENTERPRISE."

257
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:04,589
Spock: SIR, I BELIEVE
THAT STARFLEET WILL
HAVE TO BE NOTIFIED

258
00:16:04,631 --> 00:16:07,091
THAT OUR RENDEZVOUS WITH
THE STARSHIP "POTEMKIN"

259
00:16:07,133 --> 00:16:08,760
WILL NOT TAKE PLACE
AS SCHEDULED.

260
00:16:12,597 --> 00:16:13,932
MR. SPOCK,
IF YOU'D CONCENTRATE

261
00:16:13,973 --> 00:16:16,225
ON THE AREAS
FOR WHICH YOU
ARE RESPONSIBLE,

262
00:16:16,267 --> 00:16:19,520
STARFLEET COMMAND
WOULD HAVE BEEN
INFORMED ALREADY.

263
00:16:19,562 --> 00:16:22,398
SINCE THE CAPTAIN
USUALLY DEALS DIRECTLY

264
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:24,692
WITH STARFLEET
IN THESE MATTERS,

265
00:16:24,734 --> 00:16:28,404
I ASSUMED THAT
MY SUGGESTIONS MIGHT
BE DEEMED INTERFERENCE.

266
00:16:31,574 --> 00:16:33,785
INFORM STARFLEET
OF THE DELAY, LIEUTENANT.

267
00:16:33,827 --> 00:16:34,786
AYE, SIR.

268
00:16:34,828 --> 00:16:36,955
CONTINUE PRESENT COURSE.

269
00:16:36,996 --> 00:16:39,039
INCREASE SPEED
TO WARP FACTOR 6.

270
00:16:43,169 --> 00:16:46,673
I'LL LET MY RECORD
SPEAK FOR ME.

271
00:16:46,714 --> 00:16:47,924
WHY ARE YOU BEING
SO DEFENSIVE?

272
00:16:47,966 --> 00:16:49,467
THERE'S NO IMPLIED
CRITICISM OF YOU

273
00:16:49,509 --> 00:16:51,093
IN MY ORDER TO REMOVE YOU
FROM THE CASE.

274
00:16:51,135 --> 00:16:52,512
THAT IS NOT
THE REASON I'M HERE.

275
00:16:52,553 --> 00:16:54,806
I'M HERE BECAUSE
DR. COLEMAN'S RECORD

276
00:16:54,848 --> 00:16:57,433
STATES THAT
HE'S INCOMPETENT.

277
00:16:57,475 --> 00:16:59,769
THAT'S THE OPINION
OF AN INDIVIDUAL.
NO, SIR.

278
00:16:59,811 --> 00:17:01,896
THAT IS THE OPINION
OF STARFLEET
COMMAND.

279
00:17:01,938 --> 00:17:03,314
I CHECKED WITH THEM.

280
00:17:03,356 --> 00:17:06,108
AND DR. COLEMAN
WAS REMOVED
FROM HIS POST

281
00:17:06,150 --> 00:17:07,986
AS CHIEF MEDICAL
OFFICER OF HIS SHIP

282
00:17:08,027 --> 00:17:09,737
FOR ADMINISTRATIVE
INCOMPETENCE.

283
00:17:09,779 --> 00:17:12,365
THERE ARE
NO ADMINISTRATIVE
DUTIES REQUIRED HERE.

284
00:17:12,406 --> 00:17:15,117
AS WELL AS FLAGRANT
MEDICAL BLUNDERS.

285
00:17:15,159 --> 00:17:17,787
PROMOTIONS AND DEMOTIONS
CAN BE POLITICALLY
MANEUVERED.

286
00:17:17,829 --> 00:17:18,997
YOU KNOW THAT, BONES.

287
00:17:19,038 --> 00:17:22,124
NOT IN STARFLEET
HEADQUARTERS,
CAPTAIN,

288
00:17:22,166 --> 00:17:25,085
AND CERTAINLY NOT
IN THE SURGEON
GENERAL'S OFFICE.

289
00:17:28,088 --> 00:17:29,674
I'M AFRAID THE ORDER
WILL HAVE TO STAND.

290
00:17:32,802 --> 00:17:34,971
I CAN ONLY SAY...

291
00:17:35,013 --> 00:17:38,098
THAT DR. COLEMAN'S
EXPERIENCE WITH WHAT
HAPPENED ON THE PLANET

292
00:17:38,140 --> 00:17:39,934
HAD TO BE THE DECIDING
FACTOR HERE.

293
00:17:39,976 --> 00:17:43,229
I'M SURE THAT YOU CAN
APPRECIATE THAT.

294
00:17:43,270 --> 00:17:46,482
I APPRECIATE
THE FACT THAT YOU HAD
A DECISION TO MAKE.

295
00:17:46,524 --> 00:17:49,569
I ALSO FIND MYSELF
IN THAT POSITION NOW, JIM,

296
00:17:49,610 --> 00:17:52,822
AND I'M ASKING YOU TO REPORT
FOR AN EXAMINATION.

297
00:17:52,864 --> 00:17:54,949
WHY?

298
00:17:54,991 --> 00:17:56,116
WHAT DO YOU
BASE THAT ON?

299
00:17:56,158 --> 00:17:58,912
DEVELOPMENT OF EMOTIONAL
INSTABILITY

300
00:17:58,953 --> 00:18:00,955
AND ERRATIC
MENTAL ATTITUDES

301
00:18:00,997 --> 00:18:02,749
SINCE RETURNING
FROM THAT PLANET.

302
00:18:07,045 --> 00:18:08,838
YOU'LL NEVER MAKE
THAT CHARGE STICK.

303
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:11,716
ANY FOOL CAN SEE
WHY YOU'RE DOING THIS.

304
00:18:11,758 --> 00:18:15,261
I'LL LET STARFLEET COMMAND
BE THE JUDGE OF MY MOTIVES.

305
00:18:15,302 --> 00:18:19,139
I WON'T SUBMIT TO
THIS PETTY SEARCH
FOR REVENGE.

306
00:18:19,181 --> 00:18:22,560
BUT YOU WILL SUBMIT
TO STARFLEET REGULATIONS,

307
00:18:22,602 --> 00:18:24,729
AND THEY STATE
THAT THE SHIP'S SURGEON

308
00:18:24,771 --> 00:18:27,732
WILL REQUIRE FULL EXAMINATION
OF ANY CREW MEMBER

309
00:18:27,774 --> 00:18:31,110
THAT HE HAS DOUBTS ABOUT,
INCLUDING THE CAPTAIN.

310
00:18:33,237 --> 00:18:34,739
[INTERCOM WHISTLES]

311
00:18:40,536 --> 00:18:41,621
CAPTAIN KIRK HERE.

312
00:18:41,662 --> 00:18:43,372
SULU HERE, CAPTAIN.

313
00:18:43,414 --> 00:18:47,376
STARFLEET COMMAND IS
REQUESTING ADDITIONAL
DETAILS ON THE DELAY.

314
00:18:47,418 --> 00:18:48,502
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

315
00:19:15,154 --> 00:19:18,532
PULSE, PRESSURE...

316
00:19:18,574 --> 00:19:20,493
BLOOD COUNT--
ALL BODY FUNCTIONS NORMAL.

317
00:19:20,534 --> 00:19:23,203
THEN WHY AM I HERE?

318
00:19:23,245 --> 00:19:24,371
DR. McCOY?

319
00:19:26,499 --> 00:19:27,541
DR. McCOY--

320
00:19:29,418 --> 00:19:31,211
QUIET WOULD BE
BEST FOR YOU.

321
00:19:31,253 --> 00:19:32,630
WHERE IS DR. McCOY?

322
00:19:32,672 --> 00:19:33,965
I'M IN CHARGE NOW.

323
00:19:34,007 --> 00:19:35,883
BRING DR. McCOY AT ONCE.

324
00:19:35,925 --> 00:19:38,886
HE IS IN COMMAND OF
MEDICINE ON THIS SHIP.

325
00:19:38,928 --> 00:19:40,930
HE WAS TAKEN OFF YOUR CASE

326
00:19:40,972 --> 00:19:42,473
BY CAPTAIN KIRK.

327
00:19:42,515 --> 00:19:44,642
BY CAPTAIN KIRK?

328
00:19:44,684 --> 00:19:48,228
IT WAS DONE FOR
YOUR OWN PROTECTION,
DR. LESTER.

329
00:19:48,270 --> 00:19:51,398
I AM NOT JANICE LESTER.
SHE DID THIS TO ME.

330
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:53,233
NOW, HOW CAN I
MAKE YOU UNDERSTAND?

331
00:19:53,275 --> 00:19:54,819
JANICE HAS DRIVEN
HERSELF MAD

332
00:19:54,861 --> 00:19:58,031
WITH JEALOUSY, HATRED,
AND AMBITION.

333
00:19:58,072 --> 00:19:59,615
NURSE CHAPEL,

334
00:19:59,657 --> 00:20:02,035
BRING MR. SPOCK
AND DR. McCOY
TO ME AT ONCE.

335
00:20:02,076 --> 00:20:03,119
NOW,
THEY MUST BELIEVE

336
00:20:03,161 --> 00:20:04,453
I AM NOT
JANICE LESTER.

337
00:20:04,495 --> 00:20:06,080
I AM IMPRISONED
IN HER BODY,

338
00:20:06,122 --> 00:20:08,582
BUT I AM NOT
JANICE LESTER.

339
00:20:08,624 --> 00:20:12,586
SHE IS SUFFERING
FROM THE DELUSION
OF BEING CAPTAIN KIRK.

340
00:20:12,628 --> 00:20:15,048
I AM NOT
JANICE LESTER.

341
00:20:15,089 --> 00:20:18,843
THE PARANOIA
HAS BEEN DEVELOPING
FOR THE PAST 6 MONTHS.

342
00:20:18,885 --> 00:20:21,345
THE RADIATION SEEMS
TO HAVE INTENSIFIED IT.

343
00:20:21,387 --> 00:20:23,263
SHE MUST BE KEPT
SEDATED.

344
00:20:23,305 --> 00:20:24,932
SHALL I PREPARE
A MILD SEDATIVE, DOCTOR?

345
00:20:24,974 --> 00:20:26,017
OF COURSE.

346
00:20:38,237 --> 00:20:40,280
YOU ARE INSANE,
DR. LESTER.

347
00:21:03,303 --> 00:21:07,391
Lester's voice:
CAPTAIN'S LOG, STARDATE UNKNOWN.

348
00:21:07,433 --> 00:21:09,518
I HAVE LOST TRACK OF TIME.

349
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:12,021
I AM STILL HELD CAPTIVE
IN A STRANGE BODY

350
00:21:12,063 --> 00:21:15,108
AND SEPARATED
FROM ALL MY CREW.

351
00:21:15,149 --> 00:21:17,693
I MUST HAVE SOUNDED
QUITE MAD TO YOU BEFORE.

352
00:21:17,735 --> 00:21:20,529
WHAT YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH
WOULD HAVE COMPLETELY
BROKEN MOST OF US.

353
00:21:20,571 --> 00:21:22,573
WELL, I'LL
BE ALL RIGHT NOW.

354
00:21:22,615 --> 00:21:25,118
COULD I SEE
YOUR DR. McCOY?

355
00:21:25,159 --> 00:21:29,080
I'M AFRAID THAT'S AGAINST
DR. COLEMAN'S ORDERS.

356
00:21:29,122 --> 00:21:31,749
OH.

357
00:21:31,791 --> 00:21:35,836
IS A VISIT BY THAT
VERY KIND MR. SPOCK
TO BE ALLOWED?

358
00:21:35,878 --> 00:21:38,839
PERHAPS THAT CAN BE ARRANGED
BEFORE WE REACH
THE BENECIA COLONY.

359
00:21:38,881 --> 00:21:41,425
THE BENECIA COLONY?
BUT ISN'T THE "ENTERPRISE"
GOING TO RENDEZVOUS

360
00:21:41,467 --> 00:21:43,970
WITH THE "POTEMKIN"
AT BETA AURIGAE?

361
00:21:44,011 --> 00:21:46,472
WELL, FIRST WE HAVE TO LET YOU
RECUPERATE AT BENECIA.

362
00:21:49,516 --> 00:21:50,935
YOU'LL FEEL BETTER
IF YOU HAVE A LITTLE.

363
00:21:53,104 --> 00:21:54,814
WELL, I'LL TRY.
THANK YOU.

364
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,735
OH, IT IS GOOD.
THANK YOU.

365
00:22:05,866 --> 00:22:08,327
COULD I FINISH IT
SLOWLY, NURSE CHAPEL?

366
00:22:08,368 --> 00:22:10,121
WELL--
I PROMISE I'LL BE GOOD.

367
00:22:13,624 --> 00:22:16,210
WELL, I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

368
00:22:16,252 --> 00:22:17,962
I'M GLAD YOU'RE FEELING
SO MUCH BETTER.

369
00:22:31,851 --> 00:22:35,771
THESE TESTS SHOULD HELP ME
PINPOINT THE CAUSE
OF JIM'S ILLNESS.

370
00:22:35,813 --> 00:22:38,607
GOOD. KNOWLEDGE
OF THE CAPTAIN'S
ABERRANT BEHAVIOR

371
00:22:38,649 --> 00:22:39,859
IS SPREADING
THROUGH THE SHIP.

372
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:42,987
THE CREW IS BECOMING
INCREASINGLY TENSE.

373
00:22:43,029 --> 00:22:44,864
YES, WELL,
WHAT WORRIES ME MOST

374
00:22:44,905 --> 00:22:47,074
IS THAT JIM SEEMS
COMPLETELY UNAWARE

375
00:22:47,116 --> 00:22:49,285
THAT SOMETHING IS
WRONG WITH HIM.

376
00:22:49,327 --> 00:22:50,995
NOW, WE'VE GOT
TO MAKE HIM REALIZE

377
00:22:51,037 --> 00:22:52,579
THAT SOMETHING SERIOUS
IS HAPPENING

378
00:22:52,621 --> 00:22:54,832
BEFORE TREATMENT
CAN EVEN BEGIN.

379
00:22:54,874 --> 00:22:57,668
I'M AFRAID THAT IS
A FORLORN HOPE, DOCTOR.

380
00:22:57,710 --> 00:23:00,378
THE ILLNESS APPEARS
TO BE PRIMARILY MENTAL.

381
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:02,048
WELL, ONE OF US SHOULD
BE ABLE TO GET TO HIM.

382
00:23:02,089 --> 00:23:05,134
I...I DON'T KNOW.
I KEEP LOOKING
FOR AN APPROACH,

383
00:23:05,176 --> 00:23:09,763
BUT THE SPEED OF WHICH
THE ILLNESS HAS TRAVELED
MAKES IT DOUBLY DIFFICULT.

384
00:23:09,805 --> 00:23:12,099
PERHAPS THE SURGEON GENERAL'S
OFFICE SHOULD BE ALERTED.

385
00:23:12,141 --> 00:23:13,726
WELL, YOU KNOW
HEADQUARTERS, SPOCK.

386
00:23:13,767 --> 00:23:16,436
THEY'RE ONLY
INTERESTED IN RESULTS
OF SPECIFIC TESTS.

387
00:23:16,478 --> 00:23:19,315
SO FAR, ALL WE HAVE TO
OFFER ARE OUR OPINIONS.

388
00:23:19,357 --> 00:23:21,359
ARE YOU SURE THAT
THE CAPTAIN WILL COMPLY

389
00:23:21,399 --> 00:23:23,777
WITH YOUR ORDER IN
HIS PRESENT STATE OF MIND?

390
00:23:23,819 --> 00:23:26,655
I'LL USE MY MEDICAL
AUTHORITY TO ENFORCE IT
IF NECESSARY.

391
00:23:32,203 --> 00:23:35,956
DOCTOR, WE ARE TREADING
ON VERY THIN GROUND.

392
00:23:35,998 --> 00:23:39,752
ACTIONS SUCH AS THESE
MIGHT BE MISINTERPRETED.

393
00:23:39,793 --> 00:23:42,255
WELL, THEN SO BE IT.

394
00:23:42,296 --> 00:23:44,757
OUR RESPONSIBILITY
IS CLEAR.

395
00:23:44,798 --> 00:23:46,300
WHATEVER HAPPENED TO THE
CAPTAIN ON THAT PLANET

396
00:23:46,342 --> 00:23:48,261
MUST HAVE TAKEN PLACE
IN THE SHORT
SPACE OF TIME

397
00:23:48,302 --> 00:23:50,763
THAT HE WAS ALONE
WITH DR. LESTER.

398
00:23:50,804 --> 00:23:53,933
PERHAPS A CONVERSATION
WITH HER MIGHT SHED
SOME LIGHT.

399
00:23:53,974 --> 00:23:55,642
WELL, IT'S WORTH A TRY.

400
00:23:55,684 --> 00:23:58,145
WHY DON'T YOU TRY
TO GET TO DR. LESTER
WHILE I EXAMINE JIM?

401
00:24:00,814 --> 00:24:03,192
WELL...GENTLEMEN.

402
00:24:03,234 --> 00:24:04,318
I'M HERE, DOCTOR.

403
00:24:09,782 --> 00:24:12,785
SPOCK, BONES, HELP ME.
DON'T LET THEM LOCK ME
AWAY FROM YOU.

404
00:24:12,826 --> 00:24:13,953
I'VE GOT
TO TALK TO YOU--

405
00:24:19,708 --> 00:24:20,751
McCoy: JIM!

406
00:24:23,379 --> 00:24:25,798
SHE MIGHT
HAVE KILLED SOMEONE.

407
00:24:25,839 --> 00:24:26,799
PUT HER IN ISOLATION
IN HER ROOM.

408
00:24:26,840 --> 00:24:28,634
MAINTAIN
A 24-HOUR WATCH.

409
00:24:28,675 --> 00:24:31,720
NO ONE, ABSOLUTELY NO ONE,
IS TO TALK TO HER
WITHOUT MY PERMISSION.

410
00:24:31,762 --> 00:24:32,805
YES, SIR.

411
00:24:44,442 --> 00:24:45,483
CAPTAIN.

412
00:24:55,702 --> 00:24:57,413
HOW IS
THE DOCTOR?

413
00:24:57,455 --> 00:24:59,081
SHE REGAINED
CONSCIOUSNESS
VERY QUICKLY.

414
00:24:59,123 --> 00:25:01,167
GOOD. I HAVE
A FEW QUESTIONS
TO ASK HER.

415
00:25:01,208 --> 00:25:02,793
DID THE CAPTAIN
ORDER IT, SIR?

416
00:25:02,835 --> 00:25:04,920
WHY SHOULD HE?
THEY'RE
MY QUESTIONS,

417
00:25:04,962 --> 00:25:07,131
THEREFORE I AM
ORDERING IT,
LIEUTENANT.

418
00:25:07,173 --> 00:25:09,300
THE CAPTAIN SAID
THAT NO ONE IS ALLOWED
TO SPEAK TO DR. LESTER.

419
00:25:09,342 --> 00:25:10,468
HAS SUCH
AN ORDER

420
00:25:10,508 --> 00:25:13,262
EVER INCLUDED
HIS SENIOR
OFFICERS?

421
00:25:13,304 --> 00:25:15,431
NO, SIR.

422
00:25:15,473 --> 00:25:18,184
MR. SPOCK, I THINK
THE CAPTAIN MEANT

423
00:25:18,225 --> 00:25:19,435
THAT A GUARD
SHOULD BE PRESENT.

424
00:25:19,477 --> 00:25:20,811
BY ALL MEANS,
LIEUTENANT.

425
00:25:28,402 --> 00:25:31,155
THAT'S ENOUGH.
THAT'S ENOUGH.

426
00:25:31,197 --> 00:25:35,034
YOUR HEART WILL LAST
FOREVER, CAPTAIN.

427
00:25:35,075 --> 00:25:36,327
HOW AM I OTHERWISE?

428
00:25:36,369 --> 00:25:38,536
IN THE PINK,
AS USUAL.

429
00:25:38,578 --> 00:25:40,914
LIVER, KIDNEY,

430
00:25:40,956 --> 00:25:43,501
BLOOD COUNT,
METABOLIC RATE.

431
00:25:43,541 --> 00:25:45,543
EVERYTHING,
EVEN YOUR GLANDS,
FUNCTIONING

432
00:25:45,585 --> 00:25:48,088
AT THEIR USUAL,
NORMAL PEAK
OF EFFICIENCY.

433
00:25:48,130 --> 00:25:50,966
GOOD. I HOPE
YOU'RE AS PLEASED
ABOUT IT AS I AM.

434
00:25:54,345 --> 00:25:57,223
DON'T GET DRESSED YET.

435
00:25:57,264 --> 00:25:58,932
YOU SAID I WAS
IN PERFECT CONDITION.

436
00:26:01,143 --> 00:26:02,186
PHYSICALLY.

437
00:26:05,272 --> 00:26:07,483
I DON'T THINK
ANOTHER TEST IS
NECESSARY.

438
00:26:07,525 --> 00:26:10,277
THE ROBBIANI
DERMAL OPTIC IS CRUCIAL.

439
00:26:10,319 --> 00:26:13,864
IT REVEALS THE BASIC
EMOTIONAL STRUCTURE.

440
00:26:13,906 --> 00:26:15,573
YOU HAD ONE ONCE BEFORE.

441
00:26:15,615 --> 00:26:18,911
NOW I NEED ANOTHER ONE
TO COMPARE WITH THAT
PREVIOUS TEST.

442
00:26:18,952 --> 00:26:20,496
THERE SHOULD BE NO CHANGE

443
00:26:20,538 --> 00:26:23,999
IN YOUR DERMAL-OPTIC REACTIONS
TO THE COLOR WAVELENGTHS.

444
00:26:27,545 --> 00:26:29,046
[DEVICE HUMMING]

445
00:26:29,088 --> 00:26:30,297
OVER HERE, CAPTAIN.

446
00:26:36,678 --> 00:26:38,138
OVER HERE, CAPTAIN.

447
00:26:38,180 --> 00:26:41,141
COMPLETE
