671
00:38:48,827 --> 00:38:51,579
BY THE POWERS GRANTED
TO ME AS CAPTAIN OF
THE "ENTERPRISE."

672
00:38:51,621 --> 00:38:55,583
A RECESS IS DECLARED,
TO BE FOLLOWED BY A VOTE.

673
00:38:55,625 --> 00:38:57,376
SPOCK: YES, SIR,
AN IMMEDIATE VOTE

674
00:38:57,418 --> 00:39:00,839
BEFORE OUR CHIEF WITNESS
CAN BE LEFT TO DIE
ON SOME OBSCURE PLANET

675
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:02,632
WITH THE TRUTH LOCKED
AWAY INSIDE OF HER.

676
00:39:02,674 --> 00:39:06,094
SILENCE!
YOU WILL BE SILENT!

677
00:39:06,136 --> 00:39:07,220
A RECESS HAS BEEN DECLARED.

678
00:39:07,262 --> 00:39:09,555
THERE WILL BE NO
CROSS DISCUSSION.

679
00:39:09,597 --> 00:39:14,060
WHEN I RETURN,
WE WILL VOTE ON
THE CHARGE OF MUTINY.

680
00:39:14,102 --> 00:39:16,938
THE EVIDENCE PRESENTED HERE
IS THE ONLY BASIS
OF YOUR DECISION.

681
00:39:42,088 --> 00:39:43,422
SCOTTY.

682
00:39:43,464 --> 00:39:44,507
DOCTOR.

683
00:39:47,426 --> 00:39:49,262
DOCTOR...

684
00:39:49,304 --> 00:39:52,598
I'VE SEEN THE CAPTAIN
FEVERISH,

685
00:39:52,640 --> 00:39:55,143
SICK, DRUNK,

686
00:39:55,185 --> 00:39:57,979
DELIRIOUS, TERRIFIED,

687
00:39:58,021 --> 00:40:01,316
OVERJOYED, BOILING MAD.

688
00:40:01,358 --> 00:40:03,276
BUT UP TO NOW,

689
00:40:03,318 --> 00:40:06,571
I HAVE NEVER SEEN HIM
RED-FACED WITH HYSTERIA.

690
00:40:08,614 --> 00:40:11,117
I KNOW HOW
I'M GOING TO VOTE.

691
00:40:11,159 --> 00:40:13,870
I'VE BEEN THROUGH THIS
WITH SPOCK.

692
00:40:13,912 --> 00:40:16,373
HE'S NOT BEING SCIENTIFIC,
AND NEITHER ARE YOU.

693
00:40:16,414 --> 00:40:18,833
IT MAY NOT BE SCIENTIFIC,

694
00:40:18,875 --> 00:40:20,752
BUT IF MR. SPOCK
THINKS IT HAPPENED,

695
00:40:20,793 --> 00:40:22,503
THEN IT MUST BE LOGICAL.

696
00:40:22,545 --> 00:40:24,381
DON'T YOU THINK
I KNOW THAT?

697
00:40:24,422 --> 00:40:26,758
MY TESTS SHOW
THERE'S NOTHING WRONG
WITH THE CAPTAIN.

698
00:40:26,799 --> 00:40:28,009
NOW, THAT'S THE ONLY FACT

699
00:40:28,051 --> 00:40:31,554
STARFLEET'S GOING
TO BE INTERESTED IN.

700
00:40:31,596 --> 00:40:36,642
HEADQUARTERS HAS ITS PROBLEMS,
AND WE HAVE OURS...

701
00:40:36,684 --> 00:40:40,897
AND RIGHT NOW,
THE CAPTAIN OF THE "ENTERPRISE"

702
00:40:40,939 --> 00:40:44,567
IS OUR PROBLEM.

703
00:40:44,609 --> 00:40:46,945
THEY'RE GOING TO CALL FOR
THE VOTE IN A FEW MINUTES.

704
00:40:46,986 --> 00:40:50,489
LET ME PUT
ONE LAST QUESTION.

705
00:40:50,531 --> 00:40:55,661
SUPPOSE YOU VOTE WITH ME
IN FAVOR OF SPOCK.

706
00:40:55,703 --> 00:41:00,041
THAT MEANS TWO VOTES TO ONE
AND SPOCK IS FREE.

707
00:41:00,083 --> 00:41:01,793
WHAT DO YOU THINK
THE CAPTAIN WILL DO?

708
00:41:07,882 --> 00:41:09,384
I DON'T KNOW.

709
00:41:09,426 --> 00:41:12,470
YOU KNOW, ALL RIGHT.

710
00:41:12,511 --> 00:41:16,766
IT'LL STICK IN HIS CRAW.
HE'LL NEVER ACCEPT IT.

711
00:41:16,808 --> 00:41:18,601
WE DON'T KNOW THAT.

712
00:41:18,643 --> 00:41:21,396
I'LL TELL YOU, HE WON'T.

713
00:41:21,438 --> 00:41:23,648
THEN, DOCTOR,

714
00:41:23,689 --> 00:41:25,775
THAT'S THE TIME
WE MOVE AGAINST HIM.

715
00:41:27,902 --> 00:41:30,196
WE'LL HAVE TO
TAKE OVER THE SHIP.

716
00:41:30,238 --> 00:41:32,031
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT
MUTINY, SCOTTY.

717
00:41:35,076 --> 00:41:36,119
AYE.

718
00:41:39,956 --> 00:41:41,124
ARE YOU READY FOR THE VOTE?

719
00:41:46,754 --> 00:41:49,299
YES.

720
00:41:49,341 --> 00:41:50,425
I'M READY FOR THE VOTE.

721
00:41:59,267 --> 00:42:02,895
PLAY THE TAPES
OF THE CONVERSATION
IN THE CORRIDOR.

722
00:42:02,937 --> 00:42:04,939
AYE, SIR.

723
00:42:04,981 --> 00:42:07,775
SCOTT ON TAPE:
THEN'S THE TIME
WE MOVE AGAINST HIM.

724
00:42:09,402 --> 00:42:11,321
WE'LL HAVE TO
TAKE OVER THE SHIP.

725
00:42:14,324 --> 00:42:17,494
MCCOY ON TAPE:
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT
MUTINY, SCOTTY.

726
00:42:17,535 --> 00:42:20,079
SCOTT ON TAPE: AYE.

727
00:42:20,121 --> 00:42:21,706
ARE YOU READY FOR THE VOTE?

728
00:42:21,747 --> 00:42:23,958
THAT'S ENOUGH.
WE KNOW WHAT WAS SAID.

729
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:27,128
ENOUGH TO CONVICT YOU
OF CONSPIRACY
WITH MUTINEERS,

730
00:42:27,170 --> 00:42:28,338
AND YOU'RE SO CHARGED.

731
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:31,049
THE SENTENCE--DEATH.

732
00:42:31,090 --> 00:42:32,633
MR. LEMLI.

733
00:42:32,675 --> 00:42:34,593
CHEKOV: STARFLEET
EXPRESSLY FORBIDS
THE DEATH PENALTY.

734
00:42:34,635 --> 00:42:37,596
ALL MY SENIOR OFFICERS
TURNING AGAINST ME?

735
00:42:37,638 --> 00:42:39,432
THE DEATH PENALTY
IS FORBIDDEN.

736
00:42:39,474 --> 00:42:40,892
THERE'S ONLY
ONE EXCEPTION.

737
00:42:40,933 --> 00:42:43,353
GENERAL ORDER 4,
AND IT HAS NOT
BEEN VIOLATED

738
00:42:43,395 --> 00:42:45,021
BY ANY OFFICER
ON THE "ENTERPRISE."

739
00:42:45,063 --> 00:42:47,065
I AM RESPONSIBLE.

740
00:42:47,106 --> 00:42:48,941
EXECUTION WILL BE IMMEDIATE.
GO TO YOUR POSTS.

741
00:42:52,362 --> 00:42:53,946
GO TO YOUR POSTS.

742
00:42:57,242 --> 00:43:00,119
SINELLI, TAKE THEM
TO THE BRIG.

743
00:43:00,161 --> 00:43:01,204
PREPARE FOR EXECUTION.

744
00:43:06,501 --> 00:43:07,544
GO ON!

745
00:43:27,480 --> 00:43:29,274
CAPTAIN REALLY MUST
BE GOING MAD
IF HE THINKS

746
00:43:29,315 --> 00:43:31,234
HE CAN GET AWAY
WITH AN EXECUTION.

747
00:43:31,276 --> 00:43:34,529
CAPTAIN KIRK WOULDN'T
ORDER AN EXECUTION
EVEN IF HE WERE GOING MAD.

748
00:43:34,571 --> 00:43:36,114
THAT CANNOT BE
THE CAPTAIN.

749
00:43:36,155 --> 00:43:37,907
WHAT DIFFERENCE
DOES IT MAKE WHO HE IS?

750
00:43:37,949 --> 00:43:40,785
ARE WE GOING TO
ALLOW AN EXECUTION
TO TAKE PLACE?

751
00:43:40,826 --> 00:43:43,788
IF SECURITY BACKS HIM UP,
HOW WILL WE FIGHT HIM?

752
00:43:43,829 --> 00:43:47,459
I'LL FIGHT THEM
EVERY WAY
AND ANY WAY I CAN.

753
00:43:47,500 --> 00:43:49,419
LIEUTENANT LISA, INFORM
ALL SECTORS OF MY DECISION.

754
00:43:49,461 --> 00:43:51,087
HAVE EACH SECTION SEND
A REPRESENTATIVE

755
00:43:51,129 --> 00:43:53,131
TO THE PLACE OF EXECUTION
ON THE HANGAR DECK.

756
00:43:53,172 --> 00:43:55,133
MR. CHEKOV, HOW FAR
TO THE BENECIA COLONY?

757
00:43:55,174 --> 00:43:56,759
COMING WITHIN
SCANNING RANGE.

758
00:43:56,801 --> 00:43:58,761
PLOT COORDINATES
FOR ORBIT.

759
00:43:58,803 --> 00:44:02,014
MR. SULU, LOCK INTO
COORDINATES AS SOON AS
ORBIT IS ACCOMPLISHED.

760
00:44:02,056 --> 00:44:04,350
INTERMENT WILL
TAKE PLACE ON BENECIA.

761
00:44:11,274 --> 00:44:12,484
YOU HAVE RECEIVED
YOUR ORDERS.

762
00:44:16,571 --> 00:44:18,573
YOU WILL OBEY MY ORDERS!

763
00:44:18,615 --> 00:44:22,701
OR YOU'LL BE CHARGED
WITH MUTINY.

764
00:44:22,743 --> 00:44:25,746
YOU WILL OBEY
MY ORDERS OR...OR...

765
00:44:47,393 --> 00:44:49,937
OHH.

766
00:44:49,979 --> 00:44:52,857
FOR A MOMENT, I THOUGHT
I WAS UP ON THE BRIDGE.

767
00:44:52,898 --> 00:44:54,567
SPOCK: PERHAPS YOU WERE.

768
00:44:54,609 --> 00:44:58,363
THEN IT'S POSSIBLE
THE TRANSFERENCE
CAN BE BROKEN.

769
00:44:58,404 --> 00:45:00,781
WELL, IF IT HAPPENS
AGAIN, I'LL FIGHT
TO STAY THERE.

770
00:45:00,823 --> 00:45:02,992
THE BRIDGE
IS WHERE YOU BELONG.

771
00:45:03,034 --> 00:45:05,578
TO ACCOMPLISH THAT,
EACH ONE OF US MUST BE READY

772
00:45:05,620 --> 00:45:08,498
TO SEIZE ANY OPPORTUNITY
TO BREAK OUT OF HERE

773
00:45:08,540 --> 00:45:09,706
AND ATTACK.

774
00:45:36,192 --> 00:45:38,403
ARTHUR, THE TRANSFERENCE
IS WEAKENING.

775
00:45:38,444 --> 00:45:39,862
WHAT HAPPENED?

776
00:45:39,904 --> 00:45:43,908
FOR A MOMENT, I FOUND MYSELF
BACK WITH THE PRISONERS.

777
00:45:43,949 --> 00:45:47,412
I WILL NOT GO BACK
TO BEING JANICE LESTER.

778
00:45:47,453 --> 00:45:48,913
YOU MUST HELP ME
PREVENT IT.

779
00:45:48,954 --> 00:45:51,290
THE ONLY WAY
TO PREVENT
THE TRANSFERENCE

780
00:45:51,332 --> 00:45:53,084
IS BY THE DEATH
OF JANICE LESTER.

781
00:45:55,169 --> 00:45:57,129
YOU MUST CARRY OUT
THE EXECUTION.

782
00:45:57,171 --> 00:45:58,964
I CAN'T.

783
00:45:59,006 --> 00:46:00,717
I CAN'T.

784
00:46:00,757 --> 00:46:02,468
THE CREW IS IN MUTINY.

785
00:46:04,803 --> 00:46:08,224
YOU MUST KILL HER
FOR ME.

786
00:46:08,266 --> 00:46:12,311
I HAVE DONE
EVERYTHING ELSE
FOR YOU...

787
00:46:12,353 --> 00:46:14,105
BUT I WILL NOT
MURDER FOR YOU.

788
00:46:14,146 --> 00:46:15,273
THEN DO IT
FOR YOURSELF.

789
00:46:27,952 --> 00:46:30,329
IF KIRK DOESN'T DIE...

790
00:46:30,371 --> 00:46:32,373
WE'LL BOTH BE EXPOSED
AS MURDERERS.

791
00:46:35,418 --> 00:46:36,669
DOES THAT GIVE YOU
ANY CHOICE?

792
00:46:55,271 --> 00:46:57,315
THE DOSAGE SHOULD BE
DOUBLY LETHAL.

793
00:47:00,109 --> 00:47:01,152
IT IS.

794
00:47:18,043 --> 00:47:21,964
TO PREVENT ANY FURTHER
CONSPIRACY, YOU'LL BE
REMOVED TO SEPARATE CELLS.

795
00:47:22,006 --> 00:47:23,633
IF THERE'S
ANY RESISTANCE,

796
00:47:23,675 --> 00:47:27,595
YOU'LL BE GIVEN
A SEDATIVE UNTIL
YOU LEARN COOPERATION.

797
00:47:27,637 --> 00:47:28,845
DR. LESTER
WILL BE FIRST.

798
00:47:31,724 --> 00:47:32,767
FOLLOW DR. COLEMAN.

799
00:47:39,190 --> 00:47:41,484
MAY I POINT OUT, CAPTAIN--

800
00:47:41,526 --> 00:47:43,402
[COLEMAN STRUGGLING]

801
00:47:43,444 --> 00:47:45,488
KILL HIM!

802
00:47:45,530 --> 00:47:46,489
KILL HIM!

803
00:47:46,531 --> 00:47:47,573
OH!

804
00:48:12,390 --> 00:48:14,891
I'VE LOST TO THE CAPTAIN!

805
00:48:14,933 --> 00:48:17,144
I'VE LOST
TO JAMES KIRK!

806
00:48:17,186 --> 00:48:19,689
I WANT YOU DEAD!

807
00:48:19,731 --> 00:48:22,107
I WANT YOU DEAD!

808
00:48:22,149 --> 00:48:25,653
I WANT YOU
DEAD!

809
00:48:25,695 --> 00:48:26,945
[LESTER SOBBING]

810
00:48:26,987 --> 00:48:30,408
OHH...I'M NEVER GONNA BE
THE CAPTAIN.

811
00:48:30,449 --> 00:48:31,992
NEVER!

812
00:48:32,034 --> 00:48:34,787
KILL HIM...OH...

813
00:48:40,793 --> 00:48:43,003
[SOBS]

814
00:48:43,045 --> 00:48:45,339
YOU ARE...

815
00:48:45,381 --> 00:48:48,092
YOU ARE
AS I LOVED YOU.

816
00:48:48,133 --> 00:48:49,926
KILL HIM.

817
00:48:52,471 --> 00:48:53,556
CAN YOU DO
ANYTHING FOR HER?

818
00:48:57,435 --> 00:48:59,771
I'D LIKE
TO TAKE CARE OF HER.

819
00:48:59,812 --> 00:49:02,939
[LESTER SOBBING]

820
00:49:02,981 --> 00:49:04,817
OF COURSE.

821
00:49:04,859 --> 00:49:05,902
COME WITH ME.

822
00:49:18,247 --> 00:49:20,792
I DIDN'T WANT
TO DESTROY HER.

823
00:49:20,833 --> 00:49:24,086
I'M SURE WE ALL
UNDERSTAND THAT,
CAPTAIN.

824
00:49:24,128 --> 00:49:27,256
HER LIFE COULD
HAVE BEEN AS RICH
AS ANY WOMAN'S,

825
00:49:27,298 --> 00:49:28,340
IF ONLY...

826
00:49:31,636 --> 00:49:32,762
IF ONLY.
